Shield of Shadows	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ShadowAdeptClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:A shadow adept can create a mobile disk of purple-black forces as a standard action. The shiedl of shadow has the effects of a shield spell and also provides three-quarters concealment (30%% miss chanche) against attacks from the other side of the shield. As with the shield spell, the shadow adept can change the defensive direction of the shield of shadow as a free action once per round on his turn. The shadow adept can see and reach through the shield, so it dows not proveide cover or concealment to opponenents. The shield of shadow lasts 1 round per caster level per day and need not to be used all at once. Creating or dismissing the shield of shadowsa is a standard action. At 8th level, the shield also grants spell resistance of 12+the character's shadow adept level on attacks against theshadow adept that originate from the other side of the shield, as if the shadow adept were under the effect of a spell resistance spell.	KEY:Shadow Adept ~ Shield of Shadows	DESC:SR %1.|ShieldOfShadowSR			DEFINE:ShieldOfShadowSR|0					BONUS:VAR|ShieldOfShadowSR|12+ShadowAdeptLVL																	SORTKEY:Class_Shadow_Adept	SOURCEPAGE:FRCS30		
